verbose_text: Post hoc Bonferroni comparison revealed that individuals with the GG genotype produced significantly larger P2 amplitudes than individuals with the AA (p = 0.023) and AG genotypes (p = 0.019), whereas P2 amplitudes did not differ significantly between individuals with the AA and AG genotypes (p = 1.000).
